      <div class="row pt-2">
        <div class="col-sm-6">
          <h3 style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128)">WAKE THE LAKE</h3>
          <hr />
          <p>
            The disappearing lakes of Bengaluru are becoming a threat to the
            environment and the city. Wake the Lake is a flagship program that
            aims at the revival and preservation of urban and rural lakes. It
            brings together civic bodies, civil society and local communities to
            actively participate in reviving lakes and establish ownership for
            sustainability.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6">
          <img src="/img/wakelake.jpg" style="width: 90%" class="rounded" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row pt-5">
        <div class="col-sm-6">
          <img
            src="/img/One-billion-drops.jpg"
            style="width: 90%"
            class="rounded"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6">
          <h3 style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128)">ONE BILLION DROPS</h3>
          <hr />
          <p>
            The One Billion Drops is a program to enhance the depleting
            groundwater levels in and around Bengaluru by conserving rainwater.
            The project intervention involves an integrated approach where
            social, technical and environmental aspects are blended during the
            intervention phase.The goal of the program is to build 10,000
            percolation pits and thereby conserve 1 billion litres of rainwater
            every year.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row pt-5">
        <div class="col-sm-6">
          <h3 style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128)">BORN LEARNING CAMPAIGN</h3>
          <hr />
          <p>
            It’s crucial for children (0-6 years) to develop physically and
            mentally in order to be school-ready. To build awareness and foster
            holistic growth, we teamed up with government-run anganwadis in
            peri-urban and rural areas that create the opportunity for a healthy
            and productive childhood.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6">
          <img
            src="/img/born-learning-campaign.jpg"
            style="width: 90%"
            class="rounded"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row pt-5 pb-4">
