        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-6">
          <h3 style="color: rgb(0, 128, 128)">RURAL RISING</h3>
          <hr />
          <p>
            Despite strong economic growth, rural communities around Bengaluru
            still struggle to access the basic necessities. To create a positive
            impact, we work with local partners to understand the needs of these
            communities and suggest solutions to offer them a better quality of
            life.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
